Title: Valducken
Description:
Quack! Quack!

<The mother duck is alerted to your presence.>

Quack quack quack quack! Quack quack quack! Quack quack quack quack quack.

<A gurgling noise from the duck's stomach interrupts her intense quacking. She does not have much food around for her ducklings as she attends to her nest. Perhaps addressing this problem will warm her up to you?>
